data.actual_result: Discord app crashes, and the channel is not deleted. System settings: iPhone 6S Plus iOS 10.3 Beta 3 TestFlight 1.8.3(70)
data.short_description: Deleteing channels on iOS causes app crash.
data.steps_to_repro: - Tap a channel. - Tap the channel name at the top of chat. - Tap Delete Channel.
